---

<section class="py-24 bg-linear-to-br from-sage/10 to-mint/10">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
		<div class="text-center mb-16">
			<span
				class="inline-block text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-sage mb-4"
				>The Difference</span
			>
			<h2
				class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-semibold text-forest mb-4 tracking-tight"
			>
				Why Pasture-Raised Is Better
			</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				When cattle live the way nature intended—roaming open paddocks and
				grazing fresh pasture—it shows in the quality of the beef.
			</p>
		</div>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
			<!-- Natural Diet -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M17 8C8 10 5.9 16.17 3.82 21.34l1.89.66.95-2.3c.48.17.98.3 1.34.3C19 20 22 3 22 3c-1 2-8 2.25-13 3.25S2 11.5 2 13.5s1.75 3.75 1.75 3.75C7 8 17 8 17 8z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					Natural Grazing
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					Our Murray Greys spend their lives on open Snake Valley
					pastures, eating what cattle were meant to eat—fresh grass
					and natural forage.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Less Stress -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M12 21.35l-1.45-1.32C5.4 15.36 2 12.28 2 8.5 2 5.42 4.42 3 7.5 3c1.74 0 3.41.81 4.5 2.09C13.09 3.81 14.76 3 16.5 3 19.58 3 22 5.42 22 8.5c0 3.78-3.4 6.86-8.55 11.54L12 21.35z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					Low-Stress Living
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					Happy cattle produce better beef. Our herd roams freely
					without the crowding and stress of feedlot conditions,
					resulting in more tender, flavourful meat.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Better Flavour -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M12 2l3.09 6.26L22 9.27l-5 4.87 1.18 6.88L12 17.77l-6.18 3.25L7 14.14 2 9.27l6.91-1.01L12 2z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					Richer Flavour
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					Pasture-raised beef develops a deeper, more complex flavour
					profile. You'll taste the difference that comes from cattle
					raised the traditional way.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- No Hormones -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zM4 12c0-4.42 3.58-8 8-8 1.85 0 3.55.63 4.9 1.69L5.69 16.9C4.63 15.55 4 13.85 4 12zm8 8c-1.85 0-3.55-.63-4.9-1.69L18.31 7.1C19.37 8.45 20 10.15 20 12c0 4.42-3.58 8-8 8z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					No Added Hormones
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					Our cattle are never given growth hormones or routine
					antibiotics. Just pasture, fresh water, and the occasional
					scratch behind the ears.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Natural Marbling -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm0 10.99h7c-.53 4.12-3.28 7.79-7 8.94V12H5V6.3l7-3.11v8.8z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					Natural Marbling
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					Murray Greys are renowned for developing beautiful
					intramuscular fat on pasture—tender, juicy beef without
					the need for intensive finishing.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Ethical -->
			<div
				class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-forest/5 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl hover:shadow-forest/5 transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1"
			>
				<div
					class="w-14 h-14 bg-linear-to-br from-forest to-sage rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6"
				>
					<svg class="w-7 h-7 fill-mint-light" viewBox="0 0 24 24"
						><path
							d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-2 15l-5-5 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l7.59-7.59L18 8l-9 9z"
						></path></svg
					>
				</div>
				<h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-forest mb-3">
					Ethically Raised
				</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
					We believe in raising cattle with respect. Our animals live
					good lives on open pastures, cared for by family who know
					each one by sight.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-16 text-center">
			<p class="text-sm text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Pasture-raised beef from cattle that live the way nature intended.
				That's the Ferguson Livestock difference.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

